                    The Bureau was established to assist the Committee with the day-to-day management of its programme of work and
                    the projects under its responsibility.
                    Current members of the Bureau include ISTAT (Chair), Statistics Netherlands, Statistics Canada, INEGI Mexico,
                    Palestinian Central Bureau of Statistics, UK Office for National Statistics, Eurostat, OECD, and UNSD.
